276
00:21:33,990 --> 00:21:37,710
We will destroy your four pillars.

277
00:21:38,200 --> 00:21:40,409
We will brand you preferiti...

278
00:21:40,410 --> 00:21:43,909
...and sacrifice them on the altars
of science...

279
00:21:43,910 --> 00:21:47,039
...then bring your church down upon you.

280
00:21:47,040 --> 00:21:50,709
Vatican City will be consumed by light.

281
00:21:50,710 --> 00:21:55,180
A shining star at the end of
the Path of Illumination.

282
00:22:00,640 --> 00:22:02,599
It's the ancient Illuminati threat.

283
00:22:02,600 --> 00:22:05,690
Destruction of Vatican city through light.

284
00:22:05,770 --> 00:22:09,439
Four pillars,
there's your kidnapped cardinals.

285
00:22:09,440 --> 00:22:12,439
You didn't tell me they were the preferiti

286
00:22:12,440 --> 00:22:14,530
the favorites to be named the next pope.

287
00:22:16,610 --> 00:22:18,910
Play it again.

288
00:22:25,240 --> 00:22:28,130
We will destroy your four pillars.

289
00:22:29,750 --> 00:22:31,379
We will brand you preferiti...

290
00:22:31,380 --> 00:22:33,890
Wait, stop it. Stop it.

291
00:22:34,800 --> 00:22:37,350
"Brand" them.

292
00:22:38,760 --> 00:22:41,389
That's another Illuminati legend.

293
00:22:41,390 --> 00:22:46,929
This one says that there
are a set of five brands...

294
00:22:46,930 --> 00:22:48,309
...each one an ambigram.

295
00:22:48,310 --> 00:22:51,019
The first four are the fundamental
elements of science:

296
00:22:51,020 --> 00:22:53,269
Earth, air, fire and water.

297
00:22:53,270 --> 00:22:56,080
The fifth, it's a mystery.

298
00:22:57,860 --> 00:23:00,250
Maybe it's this.

299
00:23:00,610 --> 00:23:02,540
He said they'd be killed publicly.

300
00:23:02,870 --> 00:23:04,250
Yes.

301
00:23:04,490 --> 00:23:07,250
Revenge for la purga.

302
00:23:07,620 --> 00:23:09,050
"La purga"?

303
00:23:10,370 --> 00:23:13,919
Oh, jeez, you guys don't even read
your own history, do you?

304
00:23:13,920 --> 00:23:19,089
1668, the Church kidnapped
four Illuminati scientists...

305
00:23:19,090 --> 00:23:21,379
...and branded each
one of them on the chest...

306
00:23:21,380 --> 00:23:23,469
...with the symbol of the cross...

307
00:23:23,470 --> 00:23:26,219
...to purge them of their sins,
and they executed them.

308
00:23:26,220 --> 00:23:28,639
Threw their bodies
into the street as a warning...

309
00:23:28,640 --> 00:23:32,439
...to others to stop questioning Church
rulings on scientific matter.

310
00:23:32,440 --> 00:23:33,649
They radicalized them.

311
00:23:33,650 --> 00:23:36,769
The purga created a darker,
more violent Illuminati...

312
00:23:36,770 --> 00:23:39,620
...one bent on retribution.

313
00:23:40,150 --> 00:23:42,069
Look how they intend to finally get it:

314
00:23:42,070 --> 00:23:45,659
Using antimatter,
technology, to destroy the Church.

315
00:23:45,660 --> 00:23:48,250
Science obliterates religion.

316
00:23:49,370 --> 00:23:51,260
Is there any more?

317
00:23:52,500 --> 00:23:56,039
- and sacrifice them on the altars
of science...

318
00:23:56,040 --> 00:23:59,089
...then bring your church down upon you.

319
00:23:59,090 --> 00:24:02,719
Vatican City will be consumed by light.

320
00:24:02,720 --> 00:24:07,139
a shining star at the end of the Path
of Illumination.

321
00:24:07,140 --> 00:24:09,570
"Path of Illumination. "

