Your petition has been denied seven times,

325
00:24:21,360 --> 00:24:25,029
No, no. This has nothing to do with my work.
The Path of Illumination...

326
00:24:25,030 --> 00:24:28,029
...is a trail that leads to the
Church of the Illumination...

327
00:24:28,030 --> 00:24:31,289
...the place where
the Illuminati would meet in secret.

328
00:24:31,290 --> 00:24:33,840
If I can find the segno, the sign that marks
the beginning of that path

329
00:24:34,330 --> 00:24:38,499
the four churches along it...

330
00:24:38,500 --> 00:24:41,419
...may be where he intends to
murder your cardinals.

