00:29:52,820 --> 00:29:55,689
Yeah. And an obedient Catholic
who didn't think...

434
00:29:55,690 --> 00:29:57,739
...that Church and science were enemies.

435
00:29:57,740 --> 00:30:00,239
...but a different language telling
the same story.

436
00:30:00,240 --> 00:30:01,209
He wanted like minds

437
00:30:01,210 --> 00:30:03,079
to find the Church of Illumination...

438
00:30:03,080 --> 00:30:05,579
...but he couldn't exactly
advertise its location

