00:31:25,030 --> 00:31:27,999
Cardinal Strauss,
you've been informed of the situation?

461
00:31:28,000 --> 00:31:29,760
Yeah.

462
00:31:29,910 --> 00:31:30,739
My belief is we should proceed with

463
00:31:30,740 --> 00:31:33,669
the sealing of conclave.

464
00:31:33,670 --> 00:31:37,629
At this late hour?
That would be highly unorthodox.

465
00:31:37,630 --> 00:31:39,939
And yet within Church law.

466
00:31:39,940 --> 00:31:41,259
It's my power. I am Great Elector.

467
00:31:41,260 --> 00:31:43,589
The cruelest honor in Christendom.

468
00:31:43,590 --> 00:31:47,139
I have no personal ambitions, Patrick.

469
00:31:47,140 --> 00:31:51,139
Only those I hold for my Church,
St. Peter's Church...

470
00:31:51,140 --> 00:31:54,149
...which is under attack at its most
