474
00:31:59,320 --> 00:32:02,399
Oh, That is exactly what they want.

475
00:32:02,400 --> 00:32:04,239
Publicity and panic.

476
00:32:04,240 --> 00:32:07,540
No, we must not give them
oxygen for the media fire.

477
00:32:08,290 --> 00:32:10,659
But the people in St. Peter's Square-

478
00:32:10,660 --> 00:32:14,999
Care deeply about their Church, as we do.

479
00:32:15,000 --> 00:32:17,589
Their faith will sustain them.

480
00:32:17,590 --> 00:32:20,259
Their faith will not protect
