483
00:32:26,640 --> 00:32:27,599
Spoken like one who has enjoyed

484
00:32:27,600 --> 00:32:30,179
the blessings of a long and full life.

485
00:32:30,180 --> 00:32:31,849
Patrick...

486
00:32:31,850 --> 00:32:33,209
...do not confuse the power

487
00:32:33,210 --> 00:32:35,269
of the office you temporarily hold...

488
00:32:35,270 --> 00:32:38,490
...with your true place here in the Vatican.

489
00:32:40,030 --> 00:32:42,830
You were a favorite of His Holiness...

